{"id": "art-15313", "label": "Art. 15313", "title": "Art. 15313", "slug": "art-15313", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1715582890\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2076\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1715582890\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>13</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1093612109\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2075\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1093612109\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Directorii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, în sistemul unitar, respectiv\nmembrii directoratului, în sistemul dualist, sunt persoane fizice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1314149825\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2074\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1314149825\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)O persoan&#259; juridic&#259; poate fi numit&#259;\nadministrator sau membru al consiliului de supraveghere al unei <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>.\nOdat&#259; cu aceast&#259; numire, persoana juridic&#259; este obligat&#259;\ns&#259; <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> desemneze un reprezentant permanent,\npersoan&#259; fizic&#259;. Acesta este supus <span class=SpellE>acelora&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> are <span\nclass=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span> r&#259;spundere civil&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> penal&#259; ca <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> un\nadministrator sau membru al consiliului de supraveghere, persoan&#259;\nfizic&#259;, ce <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span> în nume propriu,\nf&#259;r&#259; ca prin aceasta persoana juridic&#259; pe care o reprezint&#259;\ns&#259; fie exonerat&#259; de r&#259;spundere sau s&#259; i se <span\nclass=SpellE>mic&#351;oreze</span> r&#259;spunderea solidar&#259;. Când\npersoana juridic&#259; <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> revoc&#259;\nreprezentantul, ea are <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span> s&#259;\nnumeasc&#259; în <span class=SpellE>acela&#351;i</span> timp un înlocuitor.</span></p>"}